{"tid":1432113,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"別將民意責任推在前線身上","createTime":"2019-08-08T07:05:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T13:55:26.000Z","uid":107060,"like":25,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"6019e3d0b6158b39929dea676e5c83514c4ffed9","tid":1432113,"uid":107060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T07:05:16.000Z","msg":"立場記者這段時間做得好好，可惜此媒體最後都是勸散。<br />\n<br />\n同一時間劉世良個免費YouTube 好多人追，可惜他也是掉轉槍頭，呼籲和理非進場。<br />\n<br />\n好多新入運動的朋友不明白，這班始終都是泛民體系人士，心低裡不相信流水社運威力，他們相信精英，相信妥協。<br />\n<br />\n現在社會是混亂的，但卻形勢大好，因為終於無一個香港人可以置身事外，不滿有形地宣洩出來，比人們抑壓地選擇自殺來得有生命力得多。我們在經歷陣痛，但暢快。<br />\n<br />\n那最後誰來收拾？從來主導都是政權，政權如能有智慧地回應，得到大多數人的接受，我不相信還會有人不顧一切地衝，上街的人他們也有自己的生活，沒有人想生活在槍林彈雨之下。<br />\n<br />\n什麼鼓勵和理非進場的，其實自大到不得了，誰說勇武的前線不懂做和理非會做的事，但這些信奉大台的和理非，才以為以他們之力可與政權周旋，難道又要呼召二百萬人出來遊行一次由頭來過嗎？"},{"pid":"62c516954fd545d6f99ca3aaac8e065f441bcc0b","tid":1432113,"uid":107060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T09:11:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02b3022245061c8eba26a38bf7a45cb589ba25f1","tid":1432113,"uid":289257,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T09:13:19.000Z","msg":"分化post大家唔好理"},{"pid":"a316776532b2c4d1d555afddedcedda5a9d1ba2d","tid":1432113,"uid":107060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T09:16:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d4cec7232da5d1b05064a527fa2a6510616f7f2","tid":1432113,"uid":265111,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T09:21:11.000Z","msg":"又係你呢條陳云根打手，咁早出黎發功"},{"pid":"bd42d95155fe99fe4893f19a2665dcf40a5c8d81","tid":1432113,"uid":107060,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0d4cec7232da5d1b05064a527fa2a6510616f7f2","tid":1432113,"uid":265111,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T09:21:11.000Z","msg":"又係你呢條陳云根打手，咁早出黎發功"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T09:25:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />Hi"},{"pid":"059509df3409b798613045af2d83dfb29c1d668e","tid":1432113,"uid":107060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T09:56:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><div style=\"text-align: center;\"></div>"},{"pid":"53971ad79bbd27c33e6145720dad28d7915cc318","tid":1432113,"uid":107060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T10:57:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac603d18dd276cc7074eae07ff33a69980ec5e50","tid":1432113,"uid":107060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T13:51:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcfc5f18136d640fbbe899a29890adbc7067b8c9","tid":1432113,"uid":107060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T15:15:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c925b6d81f03cabdb49a278633791ac34af54b00","tid":1432113,"uid":107060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T15:25:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2d9d32518007c61a4ee249c81ed393e4c07c1b1","tid":1432113,"uid":107060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T01:57:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e9746c2a02cbbdef3a1ca513c2f7c710a7cb09b","tid":1432113,"uid":269119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T02:02:32.000Z","msg":"包剪揼理論：<br />\n✊ = 武力優勢<br />\n✌ = 和平理念<br />\n✋ = 團結友誼<br />\n<br />\n和平理想唔可以打敗武力優勢，但係可以化敵人為友。當朋友們各展所長就可以令武力優勢孤立無援。武力都要食飯要休息。車都要入油，機械人都要充電維修,。出揼嘅除非是十項全能，自給自足，就要靠其他人。<br />\n<br />\n武力對武力唔係唔得，但係前題係自己究竟係較剪定係石頭呢？無錯，較剪夠多係可以鋤爆舊石，但係其實舊石包住咗就得㗎喇。紙太細係包唔到好多嘅石，但係較剪造紙快過鋤石。有人發現自己其實唔係剪，係包嗎？"},{"pid":"bca7d5f3abfb9850d76bf0c2d6b0e0f790404253","tid":1432113,"uid":107060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T05:45:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a93baee5efc5592c0ac583e267458f07efab1ffb","tid":1432113,"uid":107060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T07:57:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb987a7bb1dd8d851a8b9ed89ec928b934d60160","tid":1432113,"uid":282018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T08:31:05.000Z","msg":"不要大台。"},{"pid":"b47546249973bd23c02ace46719cd2752608608c","tid":1432113,"uid":107060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T11:57:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79da8473458b42a5b7882b87d27b27c8349564b1","tid":1432113,"uid":107060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T13:55:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}